title: Sovereign in that able to agree on the greatest among them.
pid: f8f6f328-4537-4a20-99b7-dcac453d8940
body: |2-
  Particularly interesting : a competitive short-term dynamic,
  feasible even among people in obviously unequal long-term positions.
  Conversation is (at least ideally, with good judges) such an arena,
  humor v. problem-solving v. inspiration ...
